# Architecture rules

**Workspace:** Open the **repo root** (`astro`, parent of `astro-coach-api` and `astro-coach-app`) as the Cursor folder. If you open only `astro-coach-app`, globs like `astro-coach-api/...` will not match any files and Cursor will show warnings — that does not break the app; it only affects when this rule auto-attaches.

Read `ai/ARCHITECTURE.md` before making changes in these directories.

Key boundaries:
- Backend routes live in astro-coach-api/src/app.ts
- AI prompts live in astro-coach-api/src/services/ai/systemPrompts.ts
- LLM calls go through generateCompletion() only — never call LLM APIs directly
- Frontend API calls go through fetchUserProfile() or direct fetch with idToken
- Profile cache lives in astro-coach-app/lib/userProfile.ts
- Feature config lives in astro-coach-app/lib/featureConfig.ts

Auth rule: Firebase only. Never suggest Clerk.
LLM rule: OpenRouter gateway. Never hardcode model names.
